// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2263 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 20d883fc-c6a8-55af-bb5e-d4f20f53bd5b

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.10*")
